title: Salisbury's Devin Irwin is the lehighvalleylive Week 7 Colonial League Defensive MVP
text:
By Brad Wilson| For lehighvalleylive.com on October 20, 2015 7:00 AM, updated October 20, 2015 9:16 AM Salisbury's Devin Irwin. (Jim Middlekauff | lehighvalleylive.com contributor) 
lehighvalleylive Colonial League Week 7 Defensive MVP 
Devin Irwin , Salisbury 
The Falcon senior linebacker had two fumble returns, of 65 and 75 yards, for touchdowns in Fridayâ€™s 39-29 defeat of visiting Northern Lehigh. He also had four tackles and a pass breakup. On offense, he ran for a 63-yard touchdown.
